menu "Virtual UART Configuration"

    config VUART_STATUS_LED_GPIO
        int "Status LED GPIO number"
        default 48
        help
            GPIO number for the addressable RGB LED (WS2812).
            Default 48 is for ESP32-S3-DevKitC. Set to your board's LED GPIO.
            Set to -1 to disable the status LED.

    config VUART_ETHERNET_ENABLED
        bool "Enable Ethernet (IP101 PHY)"
        default y
        help
            Enable Ethernet support using the internal EMAC and IP101 PHY.
            This is for the Guition JC-ESP32P4-M3-Dev board with IP101.
            Disable if your board does not have Ethernet hardware.

endmenu
